pr_body:
@hannorein
C version is working for elements_direct and elements_forces.  GR runs, but animation doesn't quite look how I'd expect it.  Need to use this gen branch together with xfgen branch on my rebound fork, and use examples/xftest/problem.c to run things.  

I'm working on updating python.

- add batch size, num units, num iterations as parser arguments
- add visualization option for inputs/outputs, which is commonly used when people try out auto-encoder for the first time

@szha @piiswrong

…t doesn't appear to be used anywhere.

@vitaly-krugl please review

fixes #879

Improve the settings messages and promote them to stable. https://github.com/swift-nav/libsbp/issues/166.

/cc @mookerji @fnoble @cbeighley 

